==考察==
斯坦利山于1906年首次登顶，山峰名源自意大利女王的名字。<ref>Peter Bridges, [http://www.vqronline.org/articles/2000/winter/bridges-prince-climbers/ ‘A Prince of Climbers’] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vqronline.org/articles/2000/winter/bridges-prince-climbers/ |date=20131112013431 }}, ''Virginia Quarterly Review'', 76-1 (Winter 2000), 38–51.</ref>.

